      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-hero ui-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"ui-hero-copy\">\n      <p class=\"ui-kicker\">AAW</p>\n      <h1>What are Universal<em>In-Ear Monitors?</em></h1>\n      <p class=\"ui-dek\">A universal in-ear monitor delivers studio-grade sound in a standardised shell. No ear impressions, no waiting \u2014 just pick a pair, choose your tips, and start listening. This article covers the concept, the history, and why AAW universal IEMs stand apart.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ui-hero-media\">\n      <img src=\"{{ 'a3h-lux-hero.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW universal in-ear monitors \u2014 immediate, portable, and reference-grade\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" loading=\"eager\">\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <div class=\"ui-stat-strip\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap ui-stats\">\n      <div class=\"ui-stat\"><b>Immediate Availability</b><span>Universals ship within days, not weeks. No impressions, no lab time \u2014 your monitor is packed and on its way the moment you order.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"ui-stat\"><b>Try Before You Buy</b><span>Audition any AAW model at our showroom or at an authorised dealer. Hear the difference between platforms before committing.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"ui-stat\"><b>Wide Selection</b><span>From the entry-level M20 dual-armature to the flagship Z07 tubeless hybrid \u2014 AAW offers universals across every price and performance tier.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"ui-stat\"><b>Portable Reference</b><span>Lightweight, compact, and driven by any source. A universal IEM is a reference listening chain that fits in a pocket.</span></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
