    "ui_benefits": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-section dark\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ui-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ui-kicker\">Benefits</p>\n        <h2>Why Choose a Universal</h2>\n        <p>A custom IEM is the ultimate in fit and isolation. But a universal IEM offers its own set of compelling advantages that make it the right choice for many listeners \u2014 including musicians who already own customs.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-benefit-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Instant Gratification</h3>\n          <p>There is no lead time. Order today, receive your monitor within days. There are no ear impressions to schedule, no lab queue, and no shipping of physical moulds to Singapore. The monitor is in stock and ready to ship.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Audition Before You Commit</h3>\n          <p>You can try a universal before you buy it. Visit the AAW showroom or an authorised dealer, listen to multiple models back-to-back, and choose the tuning that suits your ear. With a custom, you commit to the sound based on a demo universal \u2014 with a universal, the demo is the product.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Shareable</h3>\n          <p>A custom monitor fits one person. A universal can be shared with a bandmate, a colleague, or a friend. Change the tips to a fresh pair and hand it over. This makes universals ideal for studios, dealer demos, and collaborative listening.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Lower Entry Cost</h3>\n          <p>Without the labour of shell modelling, 3D printing, and hand-finishing, a universal IEM costs less than its custom equivalent. The drivers, crossover, and tuning are identical \u2014 the savings come from the standardised shell. You pay for the sound, not the fit.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Resale Value</h3>\n          <p>A used custom IEM has no market because it fits only one person. A used universal can be sold to any listener. Clean the tips, replace the cable, and it is as good as new for the next owner. Universals hold their value in a way customs cannot.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Tip Flexibility</h3>\n          <p>You are not locked into one fit. Switch between silicone for brightness, foam for isolation, or AAW\u2019s LiquidMorph tips for a semi-custom seal. Different tips change the insertion depth and bass response, giving you tonal control that a fixed custom shell cannot offer.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
