        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-section\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ui-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ui-kicker\">Comparison</p>\n        <h2>Universal vs Custom at a Glance</h2>\n        <p>Both formats use the same drivers, crossovers, and tuning targets. The difference is in the shell, the fit, and the ownership experience. Here is how they compare across the dimensions that matter most.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-compare-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell header\"><h4>Feature</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell header\"><h4>Universal IEM</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell header\"><h4>Custom IEM</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Fit</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Standardised shell with interchangeable tips; fits most ears well</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Moulded from individual ear impressions; exact anatomical fit</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Lead Time</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>In stock; ships within days</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>2\u20134 weeks from receipt of impressions</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Isolation</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>\u221215 to \u221220 dB depending on tip material and seal</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Up to \u221226 dB with full-shell passive seal</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Sound Consistency</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Varies slightly with tip choice and insertion depth</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Fixed driver-to-eardrum distance; identical every session</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Shareability</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Can be shared; change tips for a fresh fit</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Fits one person only; not shareable</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Resale Value</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Strong second-hand market; fits any listener</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Negligible; must be reshelled for a new owner</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Personalisation</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Limited to cable, tips, and standard finishes</p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>Full control over shell colour, faceplate, artwork, engraving</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell label\"><span>Best For</span></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell highlight\"><p><b>First-time buyers, auditioning, backups, sharing, quick delivery</b></p></div>\n        <div class=\"ui-compare-cell\"><p>Stage use, ultimate isolation, long-session comfort, personal investment</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
