    "ui_why_aaw": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-section dark\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ui-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ui-kicker\">Why AAW</p>\n        <h2>What Makes an AAW Universal Different</h2>\n        <p>Many brands offer universal IEMs. AAW approaches them differently \u2014 with the same driver expertise, tuning rigour, and hand-built quality control that defines our custom monitors. A universal from AAW is not a compromised product. It is the same acoustic platform in a standardised shell.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-approach-grid\" style=\"margin-top:28px;\">\n        <div class=\"ui-approach-card\">\n          <h3>Shared Acoustic Platforms</h3>\n          <p>Models like the Mockingbird, Halcyon, and A3H+ Lux are available in both universal and custom fitments. The driver count, crossover design, and tuning target are identical. When you audition a Mockingbird universal, you are hearing exactly what the custom version sounds like \u2014 the only difference is the shell.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-approach-card\">\n          <h3>Tubeless Technology</h3>\n          <p>AAW\u2019s Z Series (Z07, Z06, Z05) uses a tubeless sound path where drivers fire directly into a resonance-controlled chamber instead of through traditional acoustic tubing. This eliminates tube resonance, reduces high-frequency distortion, and delivers a more open, spacious soundstage in a universal form factor.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-approach-card\">\n          <h3>LiquidMorph Tips</h3>\n          <p>Included with select AAW universal models, LiquidMorph tips are a silicone material that softens with body heat and conforms to the shape of your ear canal over several minutes of wear. They offer a semi-custom seal without the cost or lead time of a full custom shell \u2014 bridging the gap between universal convenience and custom isolation.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-approach-card\">\n          <h3>Switchable Tuning</h3>\n          <p>The Z05 AuAg features TwinCore, a mechanical switch that alters the crossover network to shift between two distinct tunings. One switch, two monitors. This level of user control is rare in universals and reflects AAW\u2019s philosophy of putting the listener in charge of the sound.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-approach-card\">\n          <h3>FitMorph Adaptive Fit</h3>\n          <p>AAW\u2019s Z07 features FitMorph geometry \u2014 a shell shape refined across thousands of ear scans to maximise comfort across diverse ear anatomies. The result is a universal that feels closer to a custom, with pressure distributed evenly across the concha and a secure, stable fit during movement.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-approach-card\">\n          <h3>Singapore QC, Every Unit</h3>\n          <p>Every AAW universal is measured on an audio analyser for channel matching and frequency response before it leaves the workshop. There is no batch sampling. The pair you receive has been individually tested and listened to by the same team that builds our flagship customs.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-note\" style=\"margin-top:28px;\">\n        <strong>Demo the full range in Singapore</strong>\n        <p>Visit our showroom at 76 Playfair Rd, #01-03 LHK2 Building to audition every AAW universal model side by side. Compare the Z07 against the Mockingbird, hear the Z05 AuAg with both TwinCore settings, and find the tuning that fits your music. <a href=\"/pages/contact\" style=\"color:#e2b768;\">Book an appointment</a> or walk in.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
