        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-section\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ui-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ui-kicker\">Our Range</p>\n        <h2>Recommended AAW Universal IEMs</h2>\n        <p>From the accessible M20 to the flagship Z07, every AAW universal shares the same tuning philosophy: musical, fatigue-free, and built to last. Here are eight models that define the range.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-product-grid\">\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/z07\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'halcyon-studio-shell-pair.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 Tubeless Hybrid Reference Monitor\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Flagship</span>\n            <h4>Z07</h4>\n            <p>Tubeless hybrid reference with FitMorph adaptive fit. 7-driver configuration with a spacious, resolving signature.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Z07 \u2192</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/z06\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'a3h-lux-closeup.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z06 Hybrid In-Ear Monitor\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Hybrid</span>\n            <h4>Z06</h4>\n            <p>Dual isobaric dynamic woofer with balanced armatures. Lush, vibrant, and spacious \u2014 the musical all-rounder.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Z06 \u2192</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/z05-auag-launch-edition\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'a3h-lux-portrait.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z05 AuAg Launch Edition with TwinCore switch\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">TwinCore</span>\n            <h4>Z05 AuAg</h4>\n            <p>5-driver hybrid with switchable tuning. Two sound signatures in one monitor \u2014 the small universal that does everything.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Z05 AuAg \u2192</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/mockingbird\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'halcyon-precision-render.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Mockingbird nine-driver hybrid reference\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Reference</span>\n            <h4>Mockingbird</h4>\n            <p>Nine-driver hybrid reference platform. Available in universal and custom \u2014 the same acoustic engine, your choice of fit.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Mockingbird \u2192</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/halcyon\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'halcyon-studio-blue-case.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Halcyon electrostatic hybrid IEM\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Electrostatic</span>\n            <h4>Halcyon</h4>\n            <p>Electrostatic hybrid with ethereal treble extension. A specialist monitor for listeners who want air and detail above all.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View Halcyon \u2192</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/ash\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'halcyon-studio-thera-cable.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW ASH hybrid in-ear monitor\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Hybrid</span>\n            <h4>ASH</h4>\n            <p>Balanced hybrid with a natural midrange and controlled bass. A refined daily driver for long listening sessions.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View ASH \u2192</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/a3h\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'a3h-lux-paper-wide.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW A3H+ Lux three-driver hybrid\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Entry Hybrid</span>\n            <h4>A3H+ Lux</h4>\n            <p>Three-driver hybrid platform. The gateway to AAW hybrid sound \u2014 warm, engaging, and remarkably capable for its price.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View A3H+ Lux \u2192</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a class=\"ui-product-card\" href=\"/products/m20\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'a3h-lux-cable-wide.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW M20 dual armature in-ear monitor\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"ui-product-body\">\n            <span class=\"ui-product-tag\">Dual BA</span>\n            <h4>M20</h4>\n            <p>Dual balanced armature monitor. Clean, accurate, and accessible \u2014 the most affordable entry into the AAW tuning philosophy.</p>\n            <span class=\"ui-product-link\">View M20 \u2192</span>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
