    "ui_testimonials": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ui-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ui-section dark\">\n    <div class=\"ui-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ui-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ui-kicker\">Testimonials</p>\n        <h2>What Listeners Say</h2>\n        <p>AAW universal IEMs are used by musicians, engineers, and enthusiasts in over 80 countries. Here is what some of them have to say about their experience.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ui-testimonial-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ui-testimonial-card\">\n          <div class=\"ui-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n          <blockquote>I was very pleasantly surprised just how good AAW monitors are. The overall sound is quite balanced with a smooth midrange and extended treble. Build quality is excellent.</blockquote>\n          <span class=\"ui-author\">Verified Buyer \u2014 Z07</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-testimonial-card\">\n          <div class=\"ui-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n          <blockquote>Excellent product. This is my first AAW IEM and I can say I am very much impressed. The clarity and separation are outstanding \u2014 I am hearing details in tracks I have known for years.</blockquote>\n          <span class=\"ui-author\">Verified Buyer \u2014 Z05 AuAg</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-testimonial-card\">\n          <div class=\"ui-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n          <blockquote>Great fit, great isolation, great material, and good sound for the price. The LiquidMorph tips are a game changer \u2014 they really do mould to your ear after a few minutes.</blockquote>\n          <span class=\"ui-author\">Verified Buyer \u2014 Mockingbird</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-testimonial-card\">\n          <div class=\"ui-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n          <blockquote>Bass is powerful and fun. Mid and treble are very natural. The Z06 has become my daily driver \u2014 it handles everything from classical to metal without breaking a sweat.</blockquote>\n          <span class=\"ui-author\">Verified Buyer \u2014 Z06</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-testimonial-card\">\n          <div class=\"ui-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n          <blockquote>Switching between the two TwinCore modes on the Z05 is like having two different monitors. One for analytical listening, one for pure enjoyment. Build quality is flawless.</blockquote>\n          <span class=\"ui-author\">Verified Buyer \u2014 Z05 AuAg</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ui-testimonial-card\">\n          <div class=\"ui-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n          <blockquote>The A3H+ Lux punches well above its price point. Warm, engaging, and never fatiguing. This is the monitor that made me sell my previous daily driver.</blockquote>\n          <span class=\"ui-author\">Verified Buyer \u2014 A3H+ Lux</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
